data.description: 6.25% Interest Rate Assumable Mortgage!! Come see this beautiful Anderson Creek Club gated community!! This beautiful home downstairs open floorplan features a formal dining room near the entryway and a fireplace in the Livingroom, but the kitchen is what stands out! Offering granite countertops, tons of counter space, and stainless steel appliances, you will fall in love with the newly purchased LG smart refrigerator with InstaView (there's water and ice in the door, but there's also craft ice in the freezer). Upstairs, you'll find a full bath in the hall to be shared between the three guest rooms and a BEAUTIFUL ensuite in the owner's room featuring a separate shower and tub. Outside you'll notice that aside from its close proximity to the community gym, lap pool, clubhouse and golf courses, this gorgeous lot is also currently the only home selling in the neighborhood with a private backyard. This is your chance at your DREAM HOME!!
